-button MD1 - GOM C M1 Show details add to favorites ABS plastic, solid colour barrel with rubber finish, solid colour clip with glossy finish, chrome finish metal tip and push-button MD1 - GOM 30 M1 Show details add to favorites ABS plastic, solid colour barrel with rubber finish, transparent colour clip with glossy finish, chrome finish metal tip and push-button MD1 - C M2 Show details add to favorites ABS plastic, solid colours with glossy finish, gold finish metal tip and push-button MD1 - C M3 Show details add to favorites ABS plastic, solid white colour with glossy finish, rose gold finish metal tip and push-button 3/4 Technical information Print areas and tech specs Features ● retractable with return spring ● made of non-toxic, highly resistant ABS plastic ● metal tip and push-button, individually processed with diamond mirror face finish ● “Parker type” refill, blue and black ink ● available in glossy or rubberised finish ● rubberised barrel versions are only printable on the clip Modularity you can combine differently coloured parts from the same version (or code number), or elements from different versions A little sphere B push-button C clip D barrel E tip Print areas 1 pad printing 46 x 9 mm 2 pad printing 40 x 9 mm 3 screen printing 40 x 30 mm * * Not available for the following versions: - MD1 - GOM CB M1 - MD1 - GOM C M1 - MD1 - GOM 30 M1 4/4 Customisations The brands mentioned in this catalogue are the exclusive property of the respective owners. They are used for purely illustrative purposes and cannot be the object of any buying and selling transactions, under any circumstances. via vittime delle foibe 15 10088 volpiano torino italy t +39 011 970 4500 f +39 011 970 4550 maxema@maxema.com MAXEMA SRL P.IVA 05321380015 privacy policy var acceptText='Accetto'; var policy_url='/cookie_privacy_policy/en'; var cookie_message='Il sito www.maxema.com utilizza cookie esclusivamente tecnici per permettere una corretta navigazione e la completa fruizione di tu